    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>ex991.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>NEWS RELEASE DATED MAY 14, 2021\n<TEXT>\n<HTML>\n<HEAD>\n     <TITLE></TITLE>\n</HEAD>\n<BODY STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif\">\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: right\"><FONT STYLE=\"font: 8pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif\"><B>Exhibit 99.1</B></FONT></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: right\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: right\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: right\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: right\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: left\"><IMG SRC=\"logo.jpg\" ALT=\"\"></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: left\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: bold 14pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0\">Wheaton Precious Metals Announces Election of\nDirectors and Approval of Special Matters</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 12pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; text-align: right; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0\">TSX | NYSE | LSE: WPM</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 12pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0\">VANCOUVER, BC, May 14, 2021 /CNW/ - Wheaton Precious\nMetals&trade; Corp. (&quot;Wheaton&quot; or the &quot;Company&quot;) announces that the nominees listed below were elected as directors\nof Wheaton at the 2021 Annual and Special Meeting of Shareholders. Detailed results of the vote for directors of the Company held at the\nAnnual and Special Meeting of Shareholders earlier today are shown below:</P>\n\n<TABLE CELLSPACING=\"0\" CELLPADDING=\"0\" STYLE=\"width: 100%; font: 7.5pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; border-collapse: collapse\">\n  <TR>\n    <TD STYLE=\"border: Black 1pt solid; padding-left: 6pt; white-space: nowrap\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 12pt\"><B>Nominee</B></FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"white-space: nowrap; vertical-align: bottom; border-top: black 1pt solid; border-right: black 1pt solid; border-